  "reasons": "Polly can throw the gold javelin for a distance of 400 feet without holding the gemstone. When holding the gemstone, she can throw the javelin three times farther. Therefore, she can throw the javelin for a distance of 400 * 3 = 1200 feet when holding the gemstone. To stand outside of the reach of the dragon's flames, Polly needs to be at a distance greater than 1000 feet. So, the answer is 1200 - 1000 = 200 feet.",
